p, insects, and the ~10^19 soil animals. Under RP medians a chicken&#x27;s welfare range is a third of a human&#x27;s, not a fiftieth, and wild/soil invertebrates carry significant aggregate (nematode) weight, so invertebrate work dominates. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 5 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 6 no_discounting_future_humans → 7 animals_matter_a_lot" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJylWGtz2zYW%2FSt3PG1XysoUST0oKevOKLHcZtZJM7YznU6UUSASkrChCC4Amtam7m%2FfC4CUKIuuNaMviUxenHPuC7jg97OILkgWq7c8omejs3YbLi4u4E4QloDiEAryvw3%2ByBOYZr7rdSHnIo7uGc0h92b%2BrDfrzwJoSMVTCJp68TRBkLGU2TpVjCcQrhBrBC6kRPBwxUisobyhDx4siJiRnGxmq2xNElm%2B8IEkbE1iOZN8TfMVUeWbHiwylQlaLJitiVJUzHKmVrOIyZBniWLJsjTvQ8Krz2d7q0urYEtXwJFZzJXxY0LCFZCdM0wCgY8btcLfCxZTwDDtXss2KC2WRJFsgaAYW5ZQCVwYMEHPMQZkTZGDSXyuVtSG5x8S%2FUpCg%2FEaQr5OudRubA1wbRJRRMRHTBo0qUgSkZgnFNaYvNiBr9vcTO6%2Faql6OX1Iaahw4T2JMwp8YRB2aXQM2BsqFcyzDWSaRi%2BUtOrYCMbvQJIFVRto3NAo5zyCGzQiIlw1LcYvkw%2BTm%2FHd5BLmG1jShAqiqJNuysqhEVN7wXqFL1uYIWUl6XgiksH6lIRUKO34mgusmG3cpLW1QSFpGjMqHbjdrJ2YLxMuMI2N72mvBemw99g0WCZnQ%2FdHePvutbGcU0Xs01TwOZmzmCkUMufa%2BUiX%2FWe3Bd4XB65IqDhyEkEtFBqkOhOJaoHkQHV5cLHE%2FE0%2B55fj6z%2FaP3yBOY15jrWt15o80wf8HW9wOWJjbA0WckdZqGxGMIcUKxLdtxV6WdQsXGCXgLbGh%2BeKrSn8E0KiiFSCp7hMF2ySEVOcuiaJOLcIRb4bN2Qt6aZ9i7FL4C%2F3x%2FZGwL2ED1xEK5JJ%2BMtzevrhayS6wGRA2S7NIhWXTGABAV0s9H%2FIUXE6Fdg3YoMeJ1jqIcPfLXgzufrtZmITZxByypYr3X4tTD9GfY1NnahzbLZwhfHeJg5uP71%2FP775w4YE%2B8iSYKl%2Bo5FBmnNFQ2joWMH4wyX6KBjBUrERbjpwhyFZZHFcRP98vjm3vwDLmt3bONl6tNJw47AOWTPjE7%2BniUHFBsMsZwJ%2FFjUcs3vMp94bkShmSSlM%2Fjdjy2VM20ahbP%2BLRT875UPbn6ZgsAOw8HQnoOMI89uHCaQxsVzFJkEi3UD0nmJgt22K2wlBTt2a6DtLkNsgYEFZS7sHTBPUm%2F6b6cgmlyTefKTik4wwswctMoK%2B0%2FeHw86gNxx4fidwPXru2s7B7dpxXS8YDoJO13ODoOf5gdd9bJpafJI%2FbGhTBEUhawGzb1bBXsJ%2Bepqu1zZVu8yMDuJYBdvGc5oso5d80%2FrdbsUZ%2Fyjxy%2BhkycuoIpSsF8co7VTC7ntHKUXkk6UiRlUrWx%2Bj1atI7R0nla1Pl8rWFalqFb8k1XP8Qmg3OEolYp6sEjEqKmWevqjSd91CZtDFij2uw%2FL09MbK04rSnMXRPFvKF%2BX2t3