imal suffering seriously, so it requires animals_somewhat. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 5 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 6 no_discounting_future_humans → 7 animals_matter_a_lot → 8 suffering_focused" link="https://viewer.diagrams.net/?lightbox=1&amp;nav=1&amp;chrome=0#Uhttps%3A%2F%2Fraw.githubusercontent.com%2Fmorganrivers%2Ftrain_to_crazy_town%2Fmain%2Fdiagram%2Ftrain_tree__w1_2_5_6_7_8.drawio" id="w1_2_5_6_7_8"><mxCell style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontSize=11;fillColor=#e9b0a0;strokeColor=#b8402a;fontColor=#511810;dashed=1;dashPattern=8 4;strokeWidth=3;fontStyle=1;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="1361" y="271" width="323" height="140" as="geometry"/></mxCell></object><object label="Resilience erodes&lt;br&gt;nuclear deterrence&lt;br&gt;[1+2+5+6+7+11]&lt;br&gt;→ AI safety (Redwood Research)&lt;br&gt;   265k lives-eq/$1k · 21% best&lt;br&gt;   runner-up Shrimp Welfare Project · 52%&lt;br&gt;▼ 11 more worldviews" tooltip="&lt;b&gt;parochial + far_away_humans + animals_somewhat + future_humans_matter_with_discounting + no_discounting_future_humans + animals_matter_a_lot + resilience_undermines_deterrence&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Peltzman effect for civil defence: making nuclear war survivable weakens deterrence and raises the chance of war, so a resilient-food dollar partly insures against a catastrophe it also makes marginally likelier. An alternative, lower estimate for ALLFED, anchored to Rodriguez&#x27;s ~0.4%/yr US-Russia war probability. Requires future people to be in the circle. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 5 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 6 no_discounting_future_humans → 7 animals_matter_a_lot → 11 resilience_undermines_deterrence" link="https://viewer.diagrams.net/?lightbox=1&amp;nav=1&amp;chrome=0#Uhttps%3A%2F%2Fraw.githubusercontent.com%2Fmorganrivers%2Ftrain_to_crazy_town%2Fmain%2Fdiagram%2Ftrain_tree__w1_2_5_6_7_11.drawio" id="w1_2_5_6_7_11"><mxCell style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontSize=11;fillColor=#c9b3dd;strokeColor=#4a2a78;fontColor=#201040;dashed=1;dashPattern=8 4;strokeWidth=3;fontStyle=1;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="1287" y="542" width="323" height="140" as="geometry"/></mxCell></object><object label="Collapse reroll:&lt;br&gt;survivors rebuild wiser&lt;br&gt;[1+2+5+6+7+12]&lt;br&gt;→ AI safety (Redwood Research)&lt;br&gt;   265k lives-eq/$1k · 23% best&lt;br&gt;   runner-up Shrimp Welfare Project · 53%&lt;br&gt;▼ 11 more worldviews" tooltip="&lt;b&gt;parochial + far_away_humans + animals_somewhat + future_humans_matter_with_discounting + no_discounting_future_humans + animals_matter_a_lot + collapse_teaches_better_future&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Collapse-as-reroll, optimistic: survivors of a near-collapse rebuild wiser and more cautious, so much of the value of preventing a survivable collapse is recovered by the better rebuild — resilient-food work aimed at averting collapse is worth less. The opposite of collapse_degrades_future, so the two cannot be held together. Requires the undiscounted far future. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 5 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 6 no_discounting_future_humans → 7 animals_matter_a_lot → 12 collapse_teaches_better_future" link="https://viewer.diagrams.net/?lightbox=1&amp;nav=1&amp;chrome=0#Uhttps%3A%2F%2Fraw.githubusercontent.com%2Fmorganrivers%2Ftrain_to_crazy_town%2Fmain%2Fdiagram%2Ftrain_tree__w1_2_5_6_7_12.drawio" id="w1_2_5_6_7_12"><mxCell style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontSize=11;fillColor=#c9b3dd;strokeColor=#4a2a78;fontColor=#201040;dashed=1;dashPattern=8 4;strokeWidth=3;fontStyle=1;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="1213" y="813" width="323" height="140" as="geometry"/></mxCell></object><object label="Collapse reroll:&lt;br&gt;survivors stagnate&lt;br&gt;[1+2+5+6+7+13]&lt;br&gt;→ ALLFED&lt;br&gt;   2385k lives-eq/$1k · 42% best&lt;br&gt;   runner-up Shrimp Welfare Project · 37%&lt;br&gt;▼ 11 more worldviews" tooltip="&lt;b&gt;parochial + far_away_humans + animals_somewhat + future_humans_matter_with_discounting + no_discounting_future_humans + animals_matter_a_lot + collapse_degrades_future&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Collapse-as-reroll, pessimistic: survivors become durably tech-averse and stagnate, locking in a permanently degraded future close in badness to extinction — so preventing a survivable collapse is worth much more, and resilient foods (ALLFED) can overtake AI safety. The opposite of collapse_teaches_better_future. Requires the undiscounted far future. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 5 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 6 no_discounting_future_humans → 7 animals_matter_a_lot → 13 collapse_degrades_future" link="https://viewer.diagrams.net/?lightbox=1&amp;nav=1&amp;chrome=0#Uhttps%3A%2F%2Fraw.githubusercontent.com%2Fmorganrivers%2Ftrain_to_crazy_town%2Fmain%2Fdiagram%2Ftrain_tree__w1_2_5_6_7_13.drawio" id="w1_2_5_6_7_13"><mxCell style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontSize=11;fillColor=#c9b3dd;strokeColor=#4a2a78;fontColor=#201040;dashed=1;dashPattern=8 4;strokeWidth=3;fontStyle=1;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="1160" y="1084" width="323" height="140" as="geometry"/></mxCell></object><object label="Time of perils:&lt;br&gt;space settlement exits it&lt;br&gt;[1+2+5+6+7+14]&lt;br&gt;→ AI safety (Redwood Research)&lt;br&gt;   2878k lives-eq/$1k · 32% best&lt;br&gt;   runner-up Shrimp Welfare Project · 33%&lt;br&gt;(Toby Ord, Elon Musk)" tooltip="&lt;b&gt;parochial + far_away_humans + animals_somewhat + future_humans_matter_with_discounting + no_discounting_future_humans + animals_matter_a_lot + time_of_perils_exit&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Time-of-perils optimism: hazard is high during the AI / nuclear transition but collapses once decorrelated, self-sufficient settlements exist — no single catastrophe reaches them all. The window closes, the expected future stretches far past the background-hazard baseline, and x-risk reduction during the window is what unlocks it (Ord, The Precipice; the multiplanetary-backup argument). Mutually exclusive with the view that early expansion re-arms the hazard. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 5 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 6 no_discounting_future_humans → 7 animals_matter_a_lot → 14 time_of_perils_exit" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJylWG1v2zgS%2FiuD4PbOzvlFkt%2BdywFp4%2BwWl7RFkmKxqAuXlmibG0nUkVQUbzf7229ISrYcK4hx%2FtIq9OiZZ145ox8nAV2QNFTveUBPxiftNpyfn8O9ICwGxcEX5I81PmQxTFPPcbuQcREGj4xmkLkzb9ab9WeDGZ7XpOIJuN26BpjGCHQhZRolivEY%2FBXijcGBhAjurxgJNZw78sCFBREzkpH1bJVGJJbFDx6QmEUklDPJI5qtiCp%2B6cEiVamg%2BQuziChFxSxjajULmPR5GisWLwvxPsS8fD7bebuQGmzU5XBkFvKNSrRPsYjO%2BGKWUMFQij4xZaycEH8FZGsqk0Dg81qt8HnBQgroyO3Psg1Km0KCQDZAUPQ%2Bi6kELgyYoE30EIkoMmASz9WKWuf9Q6LVsW8wzsDnUcKlNnIjgO%2FGAUVEPGLSoElF4oCEPKYQYXjDFnzfRG%2Fy%2BF1T1a%2FTp4T6Cl98JGFKgS8MwjbQLQP2jkoF83QNqVajX5S0bNgYLj6AJAuq1lC7pUHGeQC3KESEv6pbjJ8nHye3F%2FeTS5ivYUljKoiirWRd5BYNmNpx1in%2B2MD4KUtJ%2BxORDNaX2KdCacMjLjCfNn6TVtY6hSRJyKhswd06aoV8GXOBQa79SHoNSEa957rBMjEbOT%2FB%2Bw9nRnJOFbGnieBzMmchU0hkzrXxgS6Mr04D3G8tuCK%2B4qiTCGqhUCDRkYhVAyQHqtODiyXGb%2FI1u7y4%2Fq39t28wpyHPMPP1uybO9AmfwzW%2BjtjoW4OFuoPUVzYiGEOK%2BYrm2%2Fy9zDMazrGGQEvjYVNnKfwTfKKIVIIn%2BJpO5zglJjl1ThLRtAh5vGu3JJJ03b5D38Xwl%2FNTey3gUcJHLoIVSSX85bZ6%2BvAMFZ1jMKAoJnSerYYJFsMNNhGmnS1QaM%2FbY%2FCMw8fQcZ7rhq%2F0SUibaVKYt0nDnB2zxyvyBxEBZOhYdJkfcu0uskCyEFmVJMZoiTVIqlRII%2FQ81D6JAD1uvIHwluUZBNTnQtCQaDVbcXR%2FjH9jOSGhsuswNg%2F1PN8umUB6QBcL%2FR86shTZRGDrQAZzTOkF8xk%2BN%2BDd5OrT7cRmp0HIKFuudAdqYI5jakVcK29iv%2FFXyGfjL7j7cnNzcfubdQw2C6sE6%2FGBBgZpzhX1oaYTAi4%2BXmIgBSNYDzaN6i24R%2FKLNAzzFGvO1037hC4Q7NEmgy06Sw17pzXIihmb%2BCONDSrR3uGpwMe8UEP2iFHQVwQqCllcEJP%2FTdkSvdg2DGX7Xyz4d6s4tE3IVAWWOVaXLnc0HGE%2BfZwABtLqyjshCXSXoI8UHbvpRdgzCerU%2FQdtZzHqNghYNVbSNrppjHyT%2FzDt2fiShOvPVHyRQXVm9lt9bzTqDHujoet1Bo5Lm04vz1an5TjuYDQcdLquMxj0XG%2FgdvMEfhE%2F7FomCfJ