lated, the astronomical future that justified x-risk work probably gets switched off long before it happens. The same expected-value reasoning that bought astronomical stakes now attenuates them: future-facing value is multiplied by the probability the simulation keeps running, and the ranking slides back toward the present. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 5 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 6 no_discounting_future_humans → 7 animals_matter_a_lot → 14 time_of_perils_exit → 16 living_in_simulation" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJy1WG1v20YS%2FisD43qVfLJMUu9yfYBjy21wdhLYDooiDpQVuRK3Jrns7tK0mrq%2F%2FWZ3SYmyaFiA0C%2BJTA6feeZ1Z%2Fb7QUDnJIvUOQ%2Fowfjg%2BBhOT0%2FhThCWgOLgC%2FLnEn%2FkCdxnnuN2IeciCh4ZzSF3p960N%2B1PB1O3O3X70JCKp%2BD2mxrjPkGsMymzOFWMJ%2BCHCDkGB1IiuB8yEmlEd%2BSBC3MipiQny2mYxSSR5QsPSMJiEsmp5DHNQ6LKNz2YZyoTtPhgGhOlqJjmTIXTgEmfZ4liyaIU70PCq8%2BnG1%2BXUoOVugKOTCO%2BUommKxbTKZ9PUyoYStEntn7bh4g9amiWTCWLs4hoq40TJsQPgaw9wSQQ%2BLRUIf6es4gCunr9Wh6D0paSIJAtEBTjwxIqgQsDJugROpDEFAkyic9VSK1vf5TolMQ3GCfg8zjlUvtgJYDfJgFFRHzEpEGTiiQBiXhCIcYEiNrwbRXfyeM3TVV%2FTp9S6iv88JFEGQU%2BNwjrVGgbsHdUKphlS8i0Gv2hpFXDxnD2HiSZU7WExg0Ncs4DuEEhIvywaTF%2BnnyY3JzdTS5gtoQFTaggirbTZZl9NECfV511iC9bGF5lKWl%2FIpLB%2Bpz4VChteMwFptvKb9LKWqeQNI0YlW24XcbtiC8SLjAHGt%2FTXgvSUe%2B5abBMzEbOD3D%2B%2FsRIzqgi9mkq%2BIzMWMQUEplxbXygS%2BeL0wL3axsuia846iSCWigUSHUkEtUCyYHq9OBigfGbfMkvzq5%2BO%2F7XV5jRiOdYGPpbE2f6hL%2BjJX6O2Ohbg4W6g8xXNiIYQ4rpjObb9L4oEh5OscRAS%2BPDI53E8B%2FwiSJSCZ7iZzrbk8wkLOicJOLIIhTxbtyQWNLl8S36LoG%2FnR%2BOlwIeJXzgIghJJuFvt93TD09Q0SkGA8paQ%2BfZYplgrVxjm2Ha2QKFtrw9Bs84fAwd57lp%2BEqfRPQoS0vzVmlYsGP2cUj%2BJCKAHB2LLvMjrt1F5kgWYquSJBgtsQRJlYpojJ6HxkcRoMeNNxDesjyBgPpcCIrVi2rW4uj%2BBP%2FGckJCVddhbB7QyHXFn3PdYTJkcLrKk4bbgpE16VNjLQoiw%2BaDxbdAdJ4tQphzUzY6AoWNzTLx33GtMgbPcTpFfl8wge4AOp%2Fr%2FxCvkkmpwE6GFs%2BwhObMZ%2Fi7Be8mlx9vJrYaDEJO2SLUDbGFNYWpHHNt7BG2Pz9E%2B1fxgdvP19dnN7%2FZQGBzskqw%2Fh9oYJBmXFEfGjoB4ezDBSaOYATrz6Ztsw132qwsioqUPpotj%2BwvdLlgj9