iplier. Mutually exclusive with the time-of-perils-exit reading. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 5 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 6 no_discounting_future_humans → 7 animals_matter_a_lot → 15 space_expansion_backfires" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJylWG1v2zgS%2FiuD4PbOzvlFkt%2BTywFp4%2BwWm3SLJEWxaAqXlmiLF0nUkVQUbzf723dISrYcK4gBf2kVefjMM6%2Bc0Y%2BjgC5IFqn3PKBHJ0fdLpydncGdICwBxcEX5I8VPuQJ3Gee4%2FYh5yIKHhnNIXdn3mwwG85GM3cADal4Cu6gqQHuEwQ6lzKLU8V4An6IeCfgQEoE90NGIg3nTjxwYUHEjORkNQuzmCSy%2FMEDkrCYRHImeUzzkKjylwEsMpUJWhyYxUQpKmY5U%2BEsYNLnWaJYsizFh5Dw6vvZ1ulSarRWV8CRWcTXKtE%2BmRKfzuhTiofQpNmc%2BA8LJqg0tk6JHwLZGMwkEPi0UiE%2BL1hEAd25%2BVl2QWmDSBDIFgiKMWAJlcCFARO0jX4iMUUeTOJ7FVLrwn9JtD3xDcYp%2BDxOudSmrgXwbBJQRMRXzFKTiiQBiXhCIcYgRx34vo7h9PG7pqqPo2XUV3jwkUQZBb4wCJtwdwzYOyoVzLMVZFqNPihp1bATOP8AkiyoWkHjhgY55wHcoBARfti0GD9PP05vzu%2BmFzBfwZImVBBFO%2BmqzDAaMLXlrGP8sYVRVJaS9iciGazPiU%2BF0obHXGBWrf0mrax1CknTiFHZgdtV3In4MuECQ934kQ5akE4Gz02DZWI2cX6C9x9OjeScKmLfpoLPyZxFTCGROdfGB7o8vjotcL914JL4iqNOIqiFQoFURyJRLZAcqE4PLpYYv%2BnX%2FOL86vfuP77BnEY8x%2FzXZ02c6RM%2BRys8jtjoW4OFuoPMVzYiGEOKCYjm2yy%2BKPIazrCSQEvjy7ZiMYV%2Fg08UkUrwFI%2FppE4yYpJT5yQRbYtQxLtxQ2JJV91b9F0Cfzk%2FdVcCHiV85CIISSbhL7cz0C9PUdEZBgPKkkLnmdp4VxTENXYTpv0tUG7H4dgEOo5n3K4fh89NQ1sJFmteW5lYEMxDXUCYQeiZdf3pIiEitrkbkj%2BICKBxQbMgoSv0cpCRqJ2Z3ESDOAu6XMyZwgxhyUJor6BLEfwUvlAsPSFj7B5SMwhNSAS6e4E68ICk0aIts8WC%2BYwmPkZHNovsu0BzMTJ0sdD%2F4eFKnFO0iIgVBjmh%2Big%2Bt%2BDd9PK3m6nNVYOQU7YMdVdqIVNMtBh7XaLa2IP8ED2wdh3cfr6%2BPr%2F53WYBtg6rBKvzgQYGac4V9aGh0wPOP15gWAUjWB02qZoduENHLbIoKhKuPV%2B17RNgJbNHmxq2BC019Ig1yIoZm%2FgjTQwq9hRM7EzgY1G2EXvEFGY2hhFLSmLy%2FxlbLiPaNQxl9z8s%2BG%2BnfGlbkqkRLHqsNV38aDjC%2FPZxCmlErK6iL5JA9wz6SNGx686EHZSgTt2N0HaWoG6DgDVkJW3bwzTlWfor055NLki0%2BkTFZxnUJ%2BmwM%2FQmk954MBm7Xm%2FkuLTtDNZZ6zjuaDIe9fquMxoNXG%2Fk9os8fhE%2F7GEmCYra1QRmD5bBVsD%2B%2BTJcpzZUm8ic7PixCrb2532yDN6yTfN3%2BhVjvL3IL4ODKS%2BDClESL%2FZh2qu43XP3YorIB1NFjCpXFu%2FD1a1QHexHFdvewVRZXKGqwugtqm6n