s_matter_with_discounting + no_discounting_future_humans + animals_matter_a_lot + space_expansion_backfires + living_in_simulation + person_affecting_view&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Person-affecting population ethics: making happy people is neutral, so the astronomical case for x-risk reduction — which rests on the sheer number of extra future lives saved from extinction — loses almost all its force. Only the harm to people who exist regardless still counts. This is the standard premise longtermism&#x27;s critics deny (discussed as the key objection in Greaves &amp; MacAskill&#x27;s &#x27;The Case for Strong Longtermism&#x27;). It requires no_discounting_future_humans, the astronomical-stakes move it pushes back on. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 5 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 6 no_discounting_future_humans → 7 animals_matter_a_lot → 15 space_expansion_backfires → 16 living_in_simulation → 17 person_affecting_view" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJzFWP9v2kgW%2F1eeots7yAKxIeCQXk5KE7JbXdqtklTVqqnoYA8wG9vjm7FD2G77t99nxjaY4KhISHe%2FRMSe%2BbzP%2B%2F6evx4EfMqyML2QAT84PTg6orOzM7pTTMSUSvIV%2B3OJH4uY7rOu4x7TQqoweBR8QQt33B33x4OxN3b7Y3cwdj1q6FQm5HpNA3MfA%2B5c6yxKUiFj8udAPSWHEqakPxcsNKDusEsuTZkaswVbjudZxGJdvugSi0XEQj3WMuKLOUvLN32aZmmmeHFhHLE05Wq8EOl8HAjtyyxORTwrjw8oltXn443b5SlvJa6AY%2BNQrkS6fdIJ8%2FmYPyW4BJXGE%2BY%2FTIXiKwR3QKF4NAJEPNYiykJmdS9fe5RwpXGTTafct0yMMa2pRsyfE1vbS2hi9H6ZzvF7KkJO8Mn6tT6i1NiDBYFukeJwpIhBRCoLpngbZmYRhxpC43k657kH%2FqFhuti3GK%2FIl1EitbHU6gDuxgEHIh4JbdF0yuKAhTLmFCFSwg59WQXC6PGLoWquwzBQChcfWZhxklOLsI6ZjgV7zXVKk2xJmRFjLmpeVeyUbudKRAl95CHigtN7Jf8Abn77l9G70c353eiSJkua8ZgrlvJOsiwDlAci3TDTIV624P40J2MsCSSL9SH2uUqNypFUCMeVxXR%2BNjcHS5JQcN2h22XUCeUslgox0via9FuUDPvfmhbLemvo%2FEQXb17ZkxOesvxpouSETUQoUhCZSKN2YLLrk9Mi93OHrpifSsiErjkUDiTGB3HaIi2Jm8CQagbPjT4tLs%2Bvfz%2F622ea8FAukDjmrvUwf8LvcInrwIZVLRZkB5mf5r6A9zgiF%2Brn4X9ZJASdIQXJnMbDdioiTj%2BTz1KmUyUTXDPZEGd5KJtoZKqdIxSebtywSPPl0S1sF9N356ejpaJHTe%2Bk