 lives saved from extinction — loses almost all its force. Only the harm to people who exist regardless still counts. This is the standard premise longtermism&#x27;s critics deny (discussed as the key objection in Greaves &amp; MacAskill&#x27;s &#x27;The Case for Strong Longtermism&#x27;). It requires no_discounting_future_humans, the astronomical-stakes move it pushes back on. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 5 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 6 no_discounting_future_humans → 7 animals_matter_a_lot → 17 person_affecting_view" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJylWG1z2kgS%2Fitdrts78ALWCyAg56tyYrybOiebsp3a2gopMkgDzFrS6GYky7qs89uvZ0YCYeQydXxxYann6adfp1vfTwK6JFmYvuMBPZmcnJ3B%2Bfk53AnCYkg5%2BIL8t8AfeQyzzLHsPuRchMEDoznk9tyZD%2BbDuTe3PWjJlCdge20FMIsR6ELKLEpSxmPw14g3AQsSIri%2FZiRUcPbYARuWRMxJTor5OotILKsXDpCYRSSUc8kjmq9JWr0ZwDJLM0HLA%2FOIpCkV85yl63nApM%2BzOGXxqhIfQszrz%2Bc7pyspb6OuhCPzkG9Uon0JFZLHc7JcUl%2FDKB9oO6fEXwPZGsskEPhUpGv8vWQhBXTl9rU8g1QZQ4JAdkBQ9D%2BLqQQuNJigXfQRiShyYBKfp2tq3PcPiXbHvsZ4Az6PEi6VmRsBPBsHFBHxEZMaTaYkDkjIYwoRBjjswbdN%2FKYP3xRVdZw%2BJmgUHnwgYUaBLzXCNtQ9DfaWyhQWWQGZUqMOSlo3bAK3a8GiBH6nIQaVwifB%2F0Rcc%2FqX6cfpzcXd9BIWBaxoTAVJaS8pqryiAUt33HSKLzsYu9SQUZ5EJI31OfapSJXJEReYSxuPSSNr3EGSJGRU9uC2iHohX8VcYIBb35NBB5Lx4KmtsXS0xtZP8O79Gy25oCkxTxPBF2TBQpYikQVXZgeqKL5YHbC%2F9uCK%2BClHnWirgUKBRMUgTjsgOVCVGFysMHLTL%2FnlxfUfZ3%2F7Cgsa8hyzXp3VEaaP%2BDss8Dhio1c1FuoOMj81scDoUcxVNN%2Fk7mWZzXCO9QNKGh92UxZR%2BBl8khKZCp7gMZXKcUZ0WqpsJKJrEMpIt25IJGlxdou%2Bi%2BGH9dNZIeBBwkcugjXJJPywewP18A0qOsdgQFVI6LxEYALE6SfKk5BeCaJTE6X23D0Bl3YtT3sdm0DPsiz3qa2Jy7VKFDSSPGBEadCtszccie%2BLTCc6xyJUuiBfo3MfGaYjiQtsHRP44VLbhpIRhGxJuwUlGBtMW67wIgyCTe3Bz%2BgTVRb3tMylSyYwR4HqulZOqkUtwXQmosCQxVilPsPfHXg7vfrtZmoyTyPklK3WqiV0MH8xbSLsV3HaxT7irzFhNq6A288fPlzc%2FGFiijSMEqyyexpopAVPqQ8tFWy4%2BHiJDhCMYK6bFGn34A69sszCsEyf7qLoml%2BAFckeTKBNQRlq2BONQUZM28QfaKxRsTdgmmYCf5ZFGLIHTEjV%2BlFRyOKKmPxPxlarkJ5phvLsnyz4V696aFqLzngsYawcVcpoOML89nEKSUiMrrK%2FkUB1AIrx